{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What once was a thriving world is now lost, shattered and forgotten.\u00a0<i>Dustbound </i>blends strategic deckbuilding with fast-paced bullet-heaven action, delivering a gameplay loop that will keep you on your toes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441420/extras/Play_your_cards.png?t=1738265096\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scavenge for cards and build your deck to adapt to any challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plan your moves carefully as you choose which cards to play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into relentless battles against waves of raiders and monsters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441420/extras/Card_Play_With_Border.gif?t=1738265096\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441420/extras/Upgrade_your_cards.png?t=1738265096\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your cards to create more powerful versions with better stats and effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the dice mechanic to apply random, permanent stat boosts to your cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stack diced stat boosts when upgrading your cards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create unique, customized cards in every run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Banish cards to gain temporary stat boosts for your character</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441420/extras/Upgrade_cards_gif_with_border.gif?t=1738265096\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph